0.Instruction: Sit in a chair in front of a table, with your forearm resting on the table, palm facing the ceiling and elbow in line with your wrist and your shoulder.

1.Instruction: Bring your right thumb to touch the tip of your index finger as much as you can

2.Instruction: Release the pinch between your right thumb and the index finger

3.Instruction: Bring your right thumb to touch your middle finger as much as you can

4.Instruction: Release the pinch between your right thumb and the middle finger

5.Instruction: Bring your right thumb to touch your ring finger as much as you can

6.Instruction: Release the pinch between your right thumb and the ring finger

7.Instruction: Bring your right thumb to touch your pinky as much as you can, trying to touch the tip of the thumb

8.Instruction: Release the pinch between your right thumb and the pinky

9.Instruction: Repeat this exercise once more for each digit
